PROBLEM DEFINITION:

Create a game in which one needs to pop balloons using an arrow to score points and reach new levels.
The game allows the user to enter his/her name and toggle audio on or off according to player's preference
and also asks the player to rate the game out of 10. Also the game displays the score and level the player reached at the end of the game.


INPUT SPECIFICATIONS:

1.	What is your Name?
2.	Do you want Audio/Sound?
3.	Will you rate your experience out of 10?


OUTPUT SPECIFICATIONS:

1.	What was your Score?
2.	Till which level did you reached?
3.	What was the reason behind your loss?


SPECIAL PROCESSING: 

1.	What if you want to quit the game in between?
2.	What if the game stops working in between?
